    "extras": [
      "October to February is the easiest weather window for this route; March and April are still workable before the desert heat spikes.",
      "India passport holders should apply on visa2egypt.gov.eg; the single-entry Egypt e-Visa is about ₹2,100.",
      "Most major archaeological sites are now effectively card-first or card-only, but keep cash for taxis, tips and small restaurants.",
      "Bargaining is expected in bazaars, and small baksheesh notes help with porters, boatmen and informal services.",
      "A 4-night Nile cruise between Luxor and Aswan can replace separate hotel stays for about ₹13,440–₹50,400 per person depending on comfort level.",
      "If diving is the priority, swap Hurghada for Sharm el-Sheikh to focus on Ras Mohammed and Tiran Island reefs.",
      "Plan Abu Simbel around February 21–22 or October 21–22 if you want the famous sun-alignment festival in the inner sanctuary."
    ],
